'From Squeak 2.1 of June 30, 1998 on 12 August 1998 at 2:43:45 pm'!"Change Set:		openInWorldFixDate:			12 August 1998Author:			Scott WallaceFixes the bug that had broken the layout of file lists and workspaces in mophic worlds; scott's bug, tracked down by John (thanks!!)"!!SystemWindow methodsFor: 'open/close' stamp: 'sw 8/12/1998 14:40'!openInWorld: aWorld	"This msg and its callees result in the window being activeOnlyOnTop"	self bounds: (RealEstateAgent initialFrameFor: self).	aWorld addMorph: self.	self activate.	aWorld startSteppingSubmorphsOf: self! !